@startuml
title Viaverse Business Mode — Activity Diagram
start
:Tap Start Business Mode;
:Check OPERATE_BUSINESS capability eligibility;
if (Allowed?) then (yes)
  :Create business profile\nname / legal type / intro;
  :Add services/categories;
  :Add packages/pricing optional;
  :Set hours + service area;
  if (Add team members?) then (yes)
    :Assign team roles;
  endif
  if (Verification required?) then (yes)
    :Submit business docs;
    :Wait for approval;
  endif
  :Start 1-month trial\nsubscription state;
  :Publish public profile;
  :Index SEO/search profile;
  :Business ready;
else (no)
  :Show reason\nsupport / appeal;
endif
stop

note bottom
Business subscription trial starts as configurable monetization state.
It must not block basic ability to send offers if marketplace policy says free offers.
end note
@enduml
